{
  "id": "local-asset-library",
  "title": "本地素材库",
  "description": "<p>把已经下到本地的素材直接浏览、搜索、拖拽到 Foundry 里。读取符合 <code>&lt;dataPath&gt;/&lt;子目录&gt;/&lt;创作者&gt;/&lt;合集&gt;/_pack_meta_*.json</code> 布局的资产清单,本机零云端调用。</p><p>支持 Image / Map / Scene / Actor / Item / Journal / Playlist / Macro / RollTable / Adventure / PDF / Audio / Icon 全部类型,自动建文件夹层级、Scene 缩略图、同包 Journal/Playlist 联动导入。</p>",
  "version": "0.4.4",
  "compatibility": {
    "minimum": "13",
    "verified": "14",
    "maximum": "14"
  },
  "esmodules": ["scripts/main.js"],
  "styles": ["styles/local-asset-library.css"],
  "authors": [{"name": "Taka", "url": "https://github.com/takaqiao"}],
  "url": "https://github.com/takaqiao/local-asset-library",
  "manifest": "https://github.com/takaqiao/local-asset-library/releases/latest/download/module.json",
  "download": "https://github.com/takaqiao/local-asset-library/releases/download/v0.4.4/module.zip",
  "flags": {
    "hotReload": {
      "extensions": ["css", "hbs", "json"],
      "paths": ["styles", "templates"]
    }
  }
}
